<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Appointment Completed - SID Clinic</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .logo {
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: white;
            margin: 0 auto 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        
        .logo img {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            object-fit: contain;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            margin: 0;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #1e3a8a;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .appointment-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d1fae5 0%, #a7f3d0 100%);
            border: 2px solid #10b981;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .appointment-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #059669 100%);
            border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
        }
        
        .appointment-card h3 {
            color: #065f46;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 12px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #a7f3d0;
        }
        
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #065f46;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            color: #1e3a8a;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-align: right;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .appointment-id {
            background-color: #1e3a8a;
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        
        .summary-section {
            background-color: #eff6ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        
        .summary-section h4 {
            color: #1e3a8a;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .summary-content {
            color: #475569;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .prescription-section {
            background-color: #fef3c7;
            border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        
        .prescription-section h4 {
            color: #92400e;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .prescription-content {
            color: #475569;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border: 1px solid #fde68a;
        }
        
        .info-box {
            background-color: #eff6ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        
        .info-box h4 {
            color: #1e3a8a;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .info-box ul {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        
        .info-box li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #475569;
        }
        
        .rating-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7 0%, #fde68a 100%);
            border: 2px solid #fbbf24;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .rating-section h4 {
            color: #92400e;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .rating-section p {
            color: #92400e;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #1e3a8a 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 25px 0;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.4);
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #1e293b;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .footer h3 {
            color: #3b82f6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .contact-info {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #334155;
        }
        
        .contact-info p {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0 10px;
                border-radius: 8px;
            }
            
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .detail-row {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                gap: 5px;
            }
            
            .detail-value {
                text-align: left;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">
                <img src="https://sidclinic.com/logo.jpeg" alt="SID Clinic Logo">
            </div>
            <h1>‚úÖ Appointment Completed</h1>
            <p>Your appointment has been successfully completed</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">Dear {{patientName}},</div>
            
            <p>Thank you for choosing <strong>SID Clinic</strong> for your healthcare needs. Your appointment with <strong>Dr. {{doctorName}}</strong> has been successfully completed.</p>
            
            <div class="status-badge">‚úÖ Completed</div>
            
            <div class="appointment-card">
                <h3>üìÖ Completed Appointment Details</h3>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">üë®‚Äç‚öïÔ∏è Doctor:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">Dr. {{doctorName}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">üìÖ Date:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{appointmentDate}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">üïê Time:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{appointmentTime}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">üè• Type:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{appointmentType}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="appointment-id">ID: {{appointmentId}}</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="summary-section">
                <h4>üìã Consultation Summary</h4>
                <div class="summary-content">{{consultationNotes}}</div>
            </div>
            
            {{#if prescription}}
            <div class="prescription-section">
                <h4>üíä Prescription</h4>
                <div class="prescription-content">{{prescription}}</div>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div class="info-box">
                <h4>üìã Follow-up Instructions</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Follow the prescribed treatment plan as directed by your doctor</li>
                    <li>Take medications as prescribed and complete the full course</li>
                    <li>Schedule any recommended follow-up appointments</li>
                    <li>Contact us immediately if you experience any adverse reactions</li>
                    <li>Keep track of your symptoms and report any changes</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="rating-section">
                <h4>‚≠ê Rate Your Experience</h4>
                <p>We value your feedback! Please take a moment to rate your experience with Dr. {{doctorName}} and our services.</p>
                <a href="{{ratingUrl}}" class="cta-button">Rate Your Experience</a>
            </div>
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="cta-button">View Appointment Summary</a>
            </div>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 25px; color: #64748b; font-size: 14px;">
                If you have any questions about your consultation, prescription, or need to schedule a follow-up appointment, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <h3>üè• SID Clinic</h3>
            <p>Providing quality healthcare services with compassion and excellence</p>
            
            <div class="contact-info">
                <p>üìß support@sidclinic.com</p>
                <p>üìû +1 (555) 123-4567</p>
                <p>üåê www.sidclinic.com</p>
                <p style="margin-top: 15px; opacity: 0.7; font-size: 12px;">
                    This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
